Amazing customer service and all around very kind person!! Susie, the manager of this shop in Baltimore helped me, not only order an ice cream cake for my daughter’s birthday, but she delivered it herself!!  I am on the other side of the country and wanted to surprise my daughter and Susie helped me make that possible and easy!!! It’s is so incredibly refreshing to come across such good people at a time when it seems like life is filled with bad!  Thank you so much, Susie, for going above and beyond!!!! 😊

The ice cream is OUTSTANDING!!!  The brand guarantees that.  Unfortunately, the service was not good on the evening my daughter and I visited. The gentlemen behind the counter were very rude to my daughter when she requested that her milkshake be remade.  Sadly, it was so thick that she could NOT drink it.  When she requested assistance, the gentleman responded "that's what you ordered!"  Honestly, how hard would it have been to add a little more liquid and mix it again.  I was sadly disappointed and will not patronize that establishment in the future.
